	(119,1,'2014-07-15 15:52:35','2014-07-15 15:52:35','<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-34\" src=\"http://administrators-mac-mini.local:5757/talara/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/img1-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"img1\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7 col-md-offset-1 red\"><strong>Talara Capital Management</strong> (“<em>Talara</em>”) is a real asset investment firm focused on the global resource and industrial sectors. Talara, through both private and public investments, takes a long-term fundamental approach with the objective of generating superior risk-adjusted returns for investors.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7\">Founded in 2011, Talara Capital Management, LLC, invests in global resource and industrial sectors through Public Equities, Structured Credit and Private Equity.  The firms Public and Private strategies together produce countless investment synergies, creating a unique set of investment opportunities that Talara  is able to leverage when partnering with companies.  This dynamic, combined with Talara\'s blend of operating, investing and structuring experience, make Talara the ideal investment partner for both Management Teams and Limited Partners.</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4 col-md-offset-1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-35\" src=\"http://administrators-mac-mini.local:5757/talara/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/img2-298x300.jpg\" alt=\"img2\" width=\"298\" height=\"300\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-36\" src=\"http://administrators-mac-mini.local:5757/talara/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/img3-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"img3\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7 col-md-offset-1\">Talara Capital Management understands the importance of being close to the center of the North American energy industry, as well as, the world’s financial center and has offices located in both New York and Houston.</div>\r\n</div>','Our Company','','inherit','open','open','','27-revision-v1','','','2014-07-15 15:52:35','2014-07-15 15:52:35','',27,'http://localhost:8888/talara/news/27-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
