	(178,1,'2014-07-17 13:45:08','2014-07-17 13:45:08','<p class=\"p1\"><strong><a href=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-64 size-medium\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Under-developed private capital market</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Small oil and gas companies in the development stage (i.e. minimal proved developed producing reserves) have a limited set of financing options, whereas larger oil and gas companies in the development stage benefit from a range of financing options (Mezz Funds, Bank Debt) tailored to the risk profile of the asset</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><strong>Under-served private equity market</strong>\r\n<i></i></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Dearth of energy-focused financial sponsors seeking that invest less than $100 million per investment</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><a href=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-64 size-medium\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><a href=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-64 size-medium\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><strong>Broader opportunity set</strong>\r\n<i></i></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Smaller “check size” provides for a greater number of investment opportunities, increasing the likelihood of identifying asymmetric transactions</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><strong>Creative deal structuring</strong>\r\n<i></i></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Less competitive private equity market allows for greater flexibility around deal structure, providing opportunity to custom tailor an investment with companies financial needs</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><a href=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-64 size-medium\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>','Private Investment','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision-v1','','','2014-07-17 13:45:08','2014-07-17 13:45:08','',9,'http://talara.local/9-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
