	(6,1,'2014-06-23 14:29:57','2014-06-23 14:29:57','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://localhost:8888/talara/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 14:29:57','2014-06-23 14:29:57','',2,'http://localhost:8888/talara/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(7,1,'2014-06-23 16:47:43','2014-06-23 16:47:43','<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n				<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-64\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"350x350\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n				<p>Real assets should be part of a diversified portfolio, especially with recent lower correlation to S&amp;P</p>\r\n				<p>Themes include: shale development, new advances in drilling and completion technology, build out of energy infrastructure, renaissance in U.S. manufacturing, and emerging market urbanization</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n				<p>Leverage knowledge of the private asset market to take advantage of public market opportunities</p>\r\n				<p>Fickle, short-term oriented public markets often create dislocations relative to private asset values</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n				<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-64\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"350x350\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n				<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-64\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"350x350\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n				<p>Record global monetary stimulus could lead to future inflation, benefiting real assets</p>\r\n				<p>Dramatic underperformance and P/E compression of cyclical companies relative to defensive companies provides an attractive entry point, as indicated in the chart below</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>','Public Investments','','publish','open','open','','public-investments','','','2014-07-17 18:41:34','2014-07-17 18:41:34','',0,'http://localhost:8888/talara/?post_type=strategy&#038;p=7',0,'strategy','',0),
	(8,1,'2014-06-23 16:47:43','2014-06-23 16:47:43','','Public Investments','','inherit','open','open','','7-revision-v1','','','2014-06-23 16:47:43','2014-06-23 16:47:43','',7,'http://localhost:8888/talara/7-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(9,1,'2014-06-23 16:47:51','2014-06-23 16:47:51','		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n				<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-64\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"350x350\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n				<strong>Under-developed private capital market</strong>\r\n				<p>Small oil and gas companies in the development stage (i.e. minimal proved developed producing reserves) have a limited set of financing options, whereas larger oil and gas companies in the development stage benefit from a range of financing options (Mezz Funds, Bank Debt) tailored to the risk profile of the asset</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n				<strong>Under-served private equity market</strong>\r\n				<p>Dearth of energy-focused financial sponsors seeking that invest less than $100 million per investment</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n				<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-64\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"350x350\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n				<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-64\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"350x350\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n				<strong>Broader opportunity set</strong>\r\n				<p>Smaller “check size” provides for a greater number of investment opportunities, increasing the likelihood of identifying asymmetric transactions</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n				<strong>Leverage knowledge of the private asset market to take advantage of public market opportunities</strong>\r\n				<p>Less competitive private equity market allows for greater flexibility around deal structure, providing opportunity to custom tailor an investment with companies financial needs</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n				<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-64\" src=\"http://talara.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/350x350-300x300.gif\" alt=\"350x350\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>','Private Investment','','publish','open','open','','private-investment','','','2014-07-17 18:40:33','2014-07-17 18:40:33','',0,'http://localhost:8888/talara/?post_type=strategy&#038;p=9',0,'strategy','',0),
