	(105,1,'2014-07-14 16:54:19','2014-07-14 16:54:19','Ganesh was most recently a Vice President in the energy investment practice at Pine Brook Road Partners. He primarily focused on the firm’s investments in the E&amp;P sector with specific responsibility for investment theme development as well as deal origination, analysis, and execution. In addition, Ganesh was responsible for the monitoring of certain portfolio investments, serving on the board of various Pine Brook portfolio companies (2011-2013).\r\n\r\nPrior to joining Pine Brook, Ganesh was an investment professional in the energy practice at CCMP Capital Advisors, both in the Houston and New York offices, where he focused on the firm\'s investments in the E&amp;P and oilfield service sectors with primary responsibility for financial modeling and analysis, transaction due diligence, and investment structuring (2008-2011).\r\n\r\nPrior to joining CCMP Capital Advisors, Ganesh was a member of the Energy Investment Banking Group at J.P. Morgan Securities, where he advised corporate clients in the E&amp;P, midstream, and oilfield service sectors on M&amp;A and capital markets transactions (2006-2008).\r\n\r\nGanesh holds a B.A. in Economics-Political Science from Columbia University (2006).\r\n\r\nGanesh serves as a Host Committee Member for the National Foundation for Veteran Redeployment, Inc. (“NFVR”), a non-profit organization founded in 2011 to assist unemployed veterans in their transition back to civilian life.\r\n\r\nBy appointment of the Office of the Mayor of Houston, Ganesh also serves on the Gulf Coast Work Force Development Board. The Gulf Coast Work Force Development Board serves 13 counties in the Houston-Galveston region and is the largest of the 28 Work Force Development Boards in Texas. The board is majority comprised of private sector members and oversees the delivery of employment services, education, and training to the constituents of the Houston-Galveston area, affecting 125,000 businesses and 5.7mm residents.','Ganesh Betanabhatla','','publish','open','open','','ganesh-betanabhatla','','','2014-07-14 16:54:19','2014-07-14 16:54:19','',0,'http://spidadesign.us/talara/?post_type=staff&#038;p=105',0,'staff','',0),
